short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Github navigation extension for Google Chrome

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Everytime I want to visit a repository homepage I need to type all repo url, or save its address on bookmarks. Its annoying, with a bad user experience. This chrome extension enable a simple and fast go to repository!
